### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Registrar nuevo usuario (crea tenant automáticamente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "tenantName": "Mi Taller"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("jwt", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
%}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("jwt", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
%}

### Obtener mi perfil (JWT requerido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Refrescar token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("jwt", response.body.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
%}

### Logout (revoca sesion en Supabase)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Obtener usuario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Actualizar mi perfil
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "username": "usuario_actualizado",
  "email": "{{email}}"
}

### Eliminar usuario (solo admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
